# Project Rules

- Always use Angular 20

- Standalone is true by default, so have to be omitted

- Never use CommonComponent

- Always use host and not @HostBinding

- Commit message max length 100 chars (total for all lines)

- Do not use window and document directly for SSR issues

- Never use :void as a type on a return function

- Never use "as unknown as" for type conversion
